      "dc:title": "ERDERA Metric - R1.3 - Metadata - Minimal VP Metadata for Level 1 Compliance",
      "http://vivoweb.org/ontology/core#abbreviation": "FM_R1-3_M_VP_L1",
      "dcat:landingPage": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/fair-metrics/erdera/FM_R1-3_M_VP_L1"
      },
      "dc:description": "The ERDERA Project has strict requirements for minimal metadata to onboard their Virtual Platform. \n                            These include: Migration away from deprecated EJP purl properties to the w3id equivalents.  Presence of the VPDiscoverable prpoperty. Properties: dcat:theme dcat:contactPoint dct:description\n                            dcat:keyword dct:language dct:license\n                            dct:publisher dct:title dcat:contactPoint dcat:landingPage.  \n                        It does not extensively test the substructure of the dct:publisher, but it must be a foaf:Agent with a foaf:name.\n",
